id: "class:rogue#agitator"
name: "Agitator"
description: "Agitators fight mightily to cast down the enemies of their ideals. Any\
  \ rogue (including the unchained rogue) can select the agitator archetype."
modifications:
- add: "ability:reputation#rogue_agitator"
